Florida State fires football coach Willie Taggart after he goes 9-12 in parts of two seasons
03 Nov 2019, 20:28 by EndPlay
TALLAHASSEE, Fla. - TALLAHASSEE, Fla. (AP) - Florida State fires football coach Willie Taggart after he goes 9-12 in parts of two seasons.
